&lt;p&gt;Anthropic’s mission is to create reliable, interpretable, and steerable AI systems. We want AI to be safe and beneficial for our users and for society as a whole. Our team is a quickly growing group of committed researchers, engineers, policy experts, and business leaders working together to build beneficial AI systems.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role Overview&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Sales Development Manager at Anthropic, you&#39;ll lead and scale our business development function to drive pipeline generation for our frontier AI products. You&#39;ll build and manage a high-performing team of BDRs, optimize our lead management processes, and collaborate closely with sales leadership to ensure alignment between pipeline generation and revenue goals. This is a critical role in scaling Anthropic&#39;s go-to-market engine during a period of hyper-growth.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build, lead, and scale a team of 8-12 BDRs focused on both inbound lead management and strategic outbound prospecting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with sales leadership to align pipeline generation with revenue targets across Startup and Enterprise segments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish and track KPIs for lead quality, conversion rates, and pipeline contribution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create comprehensive training programs and career development paths for BDRs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with marketing to optimize lead quality and campaign effectiveness&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive adoption of sales tools and technologies (Salesforce, HubSpot, SQL) to improve team efficiency&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own Pipeline Reviews with sales leadership - covering top of funnel health, conversion metrics, outbound progress, and marketing support / follow-through&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage relationships with cross-functional stakeholders including sales, marketing, and operations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build scalable processes to support Anthropic&#39;s rapid growth&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coach and mentor BDRs on prospecting strategies, qualification techniques, and career development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3-5 years of experience managing BDR teams, preferably in high-growth SaaS or technology companies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven track record of building and scaling successful BDR teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong analytical skills with experience using data to drive decision-making&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with Salesforce, HubSpot, and sales analytics tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated ability to develop and implement effective sales processes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication and leadership skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in API-first or consumption-based business models preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor&#39;s degree or equivalent work experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Preferred Experience&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience managing teams in AI/ML or developer-focused companies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Background in both inbound and outbound lead generation strategies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track record of developing BDRs who successfully transition to AE roles&lt;/li&gt;
